abstract.text: A bar chart. The BarChartVisual structure describes a visual that is a member of the bar chart family. The following charts can be described using this structure:
A table visual. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A visual displayed on a sheet in an analysis, dashboard, or template. This is a union type structure. For this structure to be valid, only one of the attributes can be defined.
A box plot. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A heat map. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A combo chart. The ComboChartVisual includes stacked bar combo charts and clustered bar combo charts For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A waterfall chart. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A tree map. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A gauge chart. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A key performance indicator (KPI). For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A histogram. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A word cloud. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A pivot table. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
An insight visual. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A visual that contains custom content. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A geospatial map or a points on map visual. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A funnel chart. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A pie or donut chart. The PieChartVisual structure describes a visual that is a member of the pie chart family. The following charts can be described by using this structure:
A scatter plot. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.

An empty visual. Empty visuals are used in layouts but have not been configured to show any data. A new visual created in the Amazon QuickSight console is considered an EmptyVisual until a visual type is selected.
A sankey diagram. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A line chart. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
A filled map. For more information, see
in the Amazon QuickSight User Guide.
